IyTh8XfRcBoUNHQw711qhvyOiHDPg8s_IbkQ7GpCrzNSNU3H8CSK-WnlDFWNKmM_0xAjJhj1JTpr456X5h5zAmA0wbnuWKmXPqPBE1ruNKtZ-xIaybMVUKqH39vzDfXzAnPMEFQLvzpGdGKpCbxSqEu46m_u0idu8Xix_w0MvlmkmrvqjxLt8HxbLC5xabF3luLtFKuWEKAmLjeTZThH_YNUEucq4G0qK_8XvxRegpN8rs7EQw4rxy4uXcc3zlXcLj3rGPtv0QwmkHGggoA5i2AAFUdarLX4vGZH_t5LEtne_33toFBs1Ld3E34rCpzfHFhOfEL4XCsNfTKm8iC2na4f89vCAefrhWWMvWpikdR062FDpveaJBnVZcCdC9XxxuIDgRiqXKIeqae7opU53WfZmx8tSYKKjiHoIi85UJI2JekvDW1MwuDcWaQehaxx8D8uqTEJoLB8ia5sLE1SKpKZzHrxZ5DJhHZAk75xmmwMNRjYdZC0zz5FTPl9VCbW-IPTjF4Dh7TGnZNtke0lh8nQtu_ZOtdp248u2K0MCbaM6TNGZ7cRxdm1RaQepN9JnVbnmc-4ByYZNWIf6TQvlBLBkhOGicnL0_vuliNpvYeczxLvEzJsXQErgoEXdOhnLKZAhZGwq-iyqxS5B5dUbJpyXwi7MF60ryZcVzcLuZwG17S1ACTKDVlVGkJ8wjpMHUUG0FJL5UwoinqRhuy634oPZ2K9IvgAgIPNTh65fdUkpeGrjPSzPz-Dn_sudE0rVDarstciIS\",\"summary\":[{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Exploring module creation**\\n\\nI’m thinking about creating an explicit named module instead of doing it automatically. I wonder if I can create a dynamic module-info without using stubs. It seems like I could make a jar with the module-info and possibly incorporate ByteBuddyAgent classes. However, I need to be cautious; using source stub/shadow classes in the real package isn't allowed. Perhaps I could utilize an upstream jar and then add the module-info?\"},{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Analyzing runtime issues**\\n\\nI’m thinking that runtime class loading might be unsupported. It seems better in native—maybe `ModuleLayer.define` could throw an UnsupportedFeatureError before the compiler? But first, we need to create a JAR. I wonder if we could avoid compiling at runtime by precompiling `module-info` as a test resource? But creating it under `src/test/java` might not work well.\\n\\nAlternatively, I could use `ModuleDescriptor.newModule(...).exports(...).requires(...).build()`, but the `ModuleInfoWriter` is internal, not public. Generating `module-info.class` bytes manually might be an option.\"}]}"}, {"type": "toolCall", "id": "call_UH4u57mSV6UIQRrb5MmsyBXi|fc_08d5b14ff114f47a016a402d7629388195948a62867c13ff63", "name": "edit", "arguments": {"path": "tests/src/net.bytebuddy/byte-buddy-agent/1.12.4/src/test/java/net_bytebuddy/byte_buddy_agent/ByteBuddyAgentTest.java", "edits": [{"oldText": "import java.io.File;\nimport java.io.IOException;\nimport java.lang.instrument.ClassDefinition;\n", "newText": "import java.io.ByteArrayOutputStream;\nimport java.io.DataOutputStream;\nimport java.io.File;\nimport java.io.IOException;\nimport java.lang.instrument.ClassDefinition;\n"}, {"oldText": "import java.util.jar.JarFile;\n", "newText": "import java.util.jar.JarEntry;\nimport java.util.jar.JarFile;\nimport java.util.jar.JarOutputStream;\n"}, {"oldText": "    private static final String ALLOW_SELF_ATTACH = \"jdk.attach.allowAttachSelf\";\n    private static final String JAVA_HOME = \"java.home\";\n", "newText": "    private static final String ALLOW_SELF_ATTACH = \"jdk.attach.allowAttachSelf\";\n    private static final String JAVA_HOME = \"java.home\";\n    private static final String ISOLATED_MODULE_NAME = \"isolated.bytebuddy.agent\";\n"}, {"oldText": "    void getInstrumentationAddsReadEdgeToSystemInstallerModule() throws Throwable {\n        try {\n            getInstrumentationFromIsolatedAgentModule();\n", "newText": "    void getInstrumentationAddsReadEdgeToSystemInstallerModule(@TempDir Path temporaryDirectory) throws Throwable {\n        try {\n            getInstrumentationFromIsolatedAgentModule(temporaryDirectory);\n"}, {"oldText": "    private static Object getInstrumentationFromIsolatedAgentModule() throws Throwable {\n        Path agentJar = resolveAgentJar();\n        ModuleFinder finder = ModuleFinder.of(agentJar);\n        ModuleReference moduleReference = finder.findAll().stream()\n                .findFirst()\n                .orElseThrow(() -> new IllegalStateException(\"Byte Buddy agent module was not found\"));\n        String moduleName = moduleReference.descriptor().name();\n", "newText": "    private static Object getInstrumentationFromIsolatedAgentModule(Path temporaryDirectory) throws Throwable {\n        Path agentJar = createExplicitModuleAgentJar(temporaryDirectory);\n        ModuleFinder finder = ModuleFinder.of(agentJar);\n        ModuleReference moduleReference = finder.find(ISOLATED_MODULE_NAME)\n                .orElseThrow(() -> new IllegalStateException(\"Byte Buddy agent module was not found\"));\n        String moduleName = moduleReference.descriptor().name();\n"}, {"oldText": "        return getInstrumentation.invoke();\n    }\n\n    private static Path resolveAgentJar() throws Exception {\n", "newText": "        return getInstrumentation.invoke();\n    }\n\n    private static Path createExplicitModuleAgentJar(Path temporaryDirectory) throws Exception {\n        Path sourceJar = resolveAgentJar();\n        Path modularJar = temporaryDirectory.resolve(\"byte-buddy-agent-explicit-module.jar\");\n        try (JarFile jarFile = new JarFile(sourceJar.toFile());\n             JarOutputStream output = new JarOutputStream(Files.newOutputStream(modularJar))) {\n            jarFile.stream().forEach(entry -> copyJarEntry(jarFile, output, entry));\n            JarEntry moduleInfo = new JarEntry(\"module-info.class\");\n            output.putNextEntry(moduleInfo);\n            output.write(moduleInfoClass());\n            output.closeEntry();\n        }\n        return modularJar;\n    }\n\n    private static void copyJarEntry(JarFile jarFile, JarOutputStream output, JarEntry entry) {\n        if (entry.getName().equals(\"module-info.class\")) {\n            return;\n        }\n        try {\n            JarEntry copy = new JarEntry(entry.getName());\n            output.putNextEntry(copy);\n            jarFile.getInputStream(entry).transferTo(output);\n            output.closeEntry();\n        } catch (IOException exception) {\n            throw new IllegalStateException(\"Cannot copy Byte Buddy agent JAR entry \" + entry.getName(), exception);\n        }\n    }\n\n    private static byte[] moduleInfoClass() throws IOException {\n        ByteArrayOutputStream output = new ByteArrayOutputStream();\n        try (DataOutputStream data = new DataOutputStream(output)) {\n            data.writeInt(0xCAFEBABE);\n            data.writeShort(0);\n            data.writeShort(53);\n            data.writeShort(17);\n            writeUtf8(data, \"module-info\");\n            writeClass(data, 1);\n            writeUtf8(data, \"Module\");\n            writeUtf8(data, ISOLATED_MODULE_NAME);\n            writeModule(data, 4);\n            writeUtf8(data, \"java.base\");\n            writeModule(data, 6);\n            writeUtf8(data, \"java.instrument\");\n            writeModule(data, 8);\n            writeUtf8(data, \"net/bytebuddy/agent\");\n            writePackage(data, 10);\n            writeUtf8(data, \"SourceFile\");\n            writeUtf8(data, \"module-info.java\");\n            data.writeShort(0x8000);\n            data.writeShort(2);\n            data.writeShort(0);\n            data.writeShort(0);\n            data.writeShort(0);\n            data.writeShort(0);\n            data.writeShort(0);\n            data.writeShort(2);\n            writeModuleAttribute(data);\n            writeSourceFileAttribute(data);\n        }\n        return output.toByteArray();\n    }\n\n    private static void writeModuleAttribute(DataOutputStream data) throws IOException {\n        data.writeShort(3);\n        data.writeInt(34);\n        data.writeShort(5);\n        data.writeShort(0);\n        data.writeShort(0);\n        data.writeShort(2);\n        data.writeShort(7);\n        data.writeShort(0x8000);\n        data.writeShort(0);\n        data.writeShort(9);\n        data.writeShort(0);\n        data.writeShort(0);\n        data.writeShort(1);\n        data.writeShort(11);\n        data.writeShort(0);\n        data.writeShort(0);\n        data.writeShort(0);\n        data.writeShort(0);\n        data.writeShort(0);\n    }\n\n    private static void writeSourceFileAttribute(DataOutputStream data) throws IOException {\n        data.writeShort(12);\n        data.writeInt(2);\n        data.writeShort(13);\n    }\n\n    private static void writeUtf8(DataOutputStream data, String value) throws IOException {\n        data.writeByte(1);\n        data.writeUTF(value);\n    }\n\n    private static void writeClass(DataOutputStream data, int nameIndex) throws IOException {\n        data.writeByte(7);\n        data.writeShort(nameIndex);\n    }\n\n    private static void writeModule(DataOutputStream data, int nameIndex) throws IOException {\n        data.writeByte(19);\n        data.writeShort(nameIndex);\n    }\n\n    private static void writePackage(DataOutputStream data, int nameIndex) throws IOException {\n        data.writeByte(20);\n        data.writeShort(nameIndex);\n    }\n\n    private static Path resolveAgentJar() throws Exception {\n"}]}}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 2203, "output": 3669, "cacheRead": 33792, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 39664, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "toolUse", "timestamp": 1782590806837, "responseId": "resp_08d5b14ff114f47a016a402d57b5ac819585742015a3475e64"}, "toolResults": [{"role": "toolResult", "toolCallId": "call_UH4u57mSV6UIQRrb5MmsyBXi|fc_08d5b14ff114f47a016a402d7629388195948a62867c13ff63", "toolName": "edit", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Successfully replaced 6 block(s) in tests/src/net.bytebuddy/byte-buddy-agent/1.12.4/src/test/java/net_bytebuddy/byte_buddy_agent/ByteBuddyAgentTest.java."}], "details": {"diff": "     ...\n  14 import org.junit.jupiter.api.BeforeEach;\n  15 import org.junit.jupiter.api.Test;\n  16 import org.junit.jupiter.api.io.TempDir;\n  17 \n+ 18 import java.io.ByteArrayOutputStream;\n+ 19 import java.io.DataOutputStream;\n  18 import java.io.File;\n  19 import java.io.IOException;\n  20 im